      {
        "id": "01f0c3b8ef5e1b30a4217455dbc40f94",
        "content": [
          "*Real_NOP always stands for the sum of Real_NOP.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "*Crypto NOP and CID NOP are client data tables.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "*When aggregating Crypto NOP + CID NOP, always group and sum by the left-side coin of each instrument (the base currency).\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "*When the instrument is in the format COIN/QUOTE (e.g., BTC/USD, BTC/EUR), ignore the quote currency and aggregate all records with the same base coin."
        ]
      }
    ]
